      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional vehicle maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior cabin, every detail confirms its status as a premier example of the marque. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this investment-grade acquisition.",
