      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This is, without question, the finest example of this model currently on the market. From the moment you lay eyes on the deep, mirror-like finish of the original factory paint\u2014completely free of swirls, chips, or road rash\u2014you\u2019ll understand its exceptional status. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the controls still retain their crisp, tactile feedback. Every electronic feature, from the immersive sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a lifetime of obsessive, preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept, never smoked in, and driven only in fair weather. It comes complete with all original keys, a full set of manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service records. For the enthusiast who demands perfection, this car offers a true 'new car' experience. It needs absolutely nothing but a driver who appreciates excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
